#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thig5.3:3.1"
msgid "3. Sīhātherīgāthā"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc77"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts77"></a>
msgctxt "thig5.3:4.1"
msgid "“Ayoniso manasikārā,"
msgstr "Afflicted with desire for sensual pleasure"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.3:4.2"
msgid "kāmarāgena aṭṭitā;"
msgstr "Due to careless attention"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.3:4.3"
msgid "Ahosiṃ uddhatā pubbe,"
msgstr "I was haughty in the past"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.3:4.4"
msgid "citte avasavattinī."
msgstr "Without mastery over the mind"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc78"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts78"></a>
msgctxt "thig5.3:5.1"
msgid "Pariyuṭṭhitā klesehi,"
msgstr "Pervaded by defilements"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.3:5.2"
msgid "subhasaññānuvattinī;"
msgstr "Following perceptions of the beautiful"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.3:5.3"
msgid "Samaṃ cittassa na labhiṃ,"
msgstr "I didn't gain peace of mind"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.3:5.4"
msgid "rāgacittavasānugā."
msgstr "Following thoughts of passion"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc79"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts79"></a>
msgctxt "thig5.3:6.1"
msgid "Kisā paṇḍu vivaṇṇā ca,"
msgstr "Lean, pale, feeble"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.3:6.2"
msgid "satta vassāni cārihaṃ;"
msgstr "I wandered for seven years"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.3:6.3"
msgid "Nāhaṃ divā vā rattiṃ vā,"
msgstr "Under much suffering"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.3:6.4"
msgid "sukhaṃ vindiṃ sudukkhitā."
msgstr "Knowing happiness neither day nor night"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="4"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc80"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts80"></a>
msgctxt "thig5.3:7.1"
msgid "Tato rajjuṃ gahetvāna,"
msgstr "Having taken a rope"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.3:7.2"
msgid "pāvisiṃ vanamantaraṃ;"
msgstr "I entered the forest"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.3:7.3"
msgid "Varaṃ me idha ubbandhaṃ,"
msgstr "[Thinking] “It’s better to hang myself"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.3:7.4"
msgid "yañca hīnaṃ punācare."
msgstr "Than to live a low life again”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="5"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc81"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts81"></a><a
#. class="pts" id="pts132"></a>
msgctxt "thig5.3:8.1"
msgid "<span class=\"var\" title=\"daḷhaṃ pāsaṃ (bj)\" id=\"note33\">Daḷhapāsaṃ</span> karitvāna,"
msgstr "Having made a strong noose"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.3:8.2"
msgid "rukkhasākhāya bandhiya;"
msgstr "Tied to the branch of a tree"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.3:8.3"
msgid "Pakkhipiṃ pāsaṃ gīvāyaṃ,"
msgstr "Putting it round my neck"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.3:8.4"
msgid "atha cittaṃ vimucci me”ti."
msgstr "My mind was then liberated"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta"><a class="sc" id="6"></a>
msgctxt "thig5.3:9.1"
msgid "…"
msgstr ""

